# Medicine Recommendation System 💊

## 📌 Overview
The Medicine Recommendation System is a Machine Learning based healthcare application that predicts suitable medicines based on user symptoms and medical datasets. The project uses intelligent algorithms to analyze symptoms and provide quick medicine recommendations, helping improve healthcare accessibility and preliminary diagnosis support.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Predict suitable medicines using symptoms
- Provide quick healthcare recommendations
- Reduce manual effort in medicine identification
- Improve healthcare accessibility using AI

---

## ✨ Features
- 💊 Symptom-Based Medicine Recommendation
- 🤖 Machine Learning Prediction Models
- 📊 Data Analysis & Visualization
- ⚡ Fast and Accurate Predictions
- 🖥️ User-Friendly Interface
- 📂 Healthcare Dataset Processing

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

### Programming Language
- Python

### Libraries & Frameworks
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Streamlit / Flask

---

## 🤖 Machine Learning Algorithms
- Decision Tree
- Random Forest
- Logistic Regression
- Naive Bayes

---

